-- Orica, Nuplex May Combine Chemical Trading Platforms, Herald Sun Reports
-- Tim Smith
-- 2010-07-06T23:04:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-06/orica-nuplex-may-combine-chemical-trading-platforms-herald-sun-reports.html

          
          
             Orica Ltd. is in talks with Nuplex 
Industries Ltd. about combining chemical trading platforms, the
Herald Sun newspaper reported, citing industry sources. A 
combined business may fetch between A$450 million to A$650 
million, according to the report.  
